OL,5,Cpromises
OL,7,FThe Housing Support Grant (HSG), which
OL,8,Ffunds homelessness services in Wales,
OL,9,Fhas been frozen since 2021, resulting
OL,10,Fin frontline worker wages falling
OL,11,Fbelow the upcoming minimum wage
OL,12,Fincrease in April.
OL,14,FThe Welsh government intends the
OL,15,Ffreeze the grant once again when its
OL,16,Fbudget is published on February 27.
