OL,7,FCharities wrote to the first minister
OL,8,Fthree weeks ago to urge him to take
OL,9,Faction, and received a response this
OL,10,Fmorning in which he said the Welsh
OL,11,Fgovernment has had to make "stark and
OL,12,Fpainful decisions".
OL,14,FWhile acknowledging the "important
OL,15,Fwork that the homelessness and housing
OL,16,Fsupport workforce do," he did not
OL,17,Fcommit to providing funding to enable
OL,18,Fcharities to pay their staff the Real
OL,19,FLiving Wage of #12 an hour.
